<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٦١٣ - خ س س]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خسَّسَ يخسِّس، تخسيسًا، فهو مخسِّس، والمفعول مخسَّس<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• خسَّس نصيبَه:</span> خَسَّه قَلَّله.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• خسَّس جسمَه:</span> أنقص وزنَه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>